caption:
"A possibly rubber duck-type object with yellow coloring and rounded shape. Smooth texture with minimal structural features. Likely a bath toy. Floating in the sink near the faucet."

"A glossy ceramic sink with white coloring and oval shape. Has a smooth basin and curved edges. Made for washing hands and face. Positioned under a mirror with toiletries nearby."

"Inconclusive evidence for the category of the object in the green bounding box. Appears to be part of a white cabinet with metallic handles. The material seems to be painted wood or laminate. Possibly a storage unit in a bathroom setting."
